name: "Entering the Dream" (Artificial Dreams Gallery #001)
description:
The author's memories (his photographs) were used as a training dataset for the AI model "MERZmory". What you see here are new re-interpretations of the authors' life.

Read more about MERZmory here: https://towardsdatascience.com/visual-ai-trained-on-my-memories-a54c55967c28?sk=3e37e2716ccee2101ba07025e5bcfd60

2048 x 2048
